    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Software\" title=\"Software\">Software</a> * <a href=\"/Databases\" title=\"Databases\">Databases</a> * Scidb</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"http://scidb.sourceforge.net/screenshots.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/40/Scidb.jpg/300px-Scidb.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"243\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/4/40/Scidb.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Scidb.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Scidb GUI <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Scidb</b>,<br />\na multi-platform, open source chess database with <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Gregor_Cramer&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Gregor Cramer (page does not exist)\">Gregor Cramer</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, inspired by <a href=\"/Shane_Hudson\" title=\"Shane Hudson\">Shane Hudson's</a> <a href=\"/SCID\" title=\"SCID\">SCID</a>, but a completely new development, written in <a href=\"/index.php?title=Tcl-Tk&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Tcl-Tk (page does not exist)\">Tcl/Tk</a> and <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a>. \nScidb features multiple chess variants, such as <a href=\"/Chess960\" title=\"Chess960\">Chess960</a>, and supports various file formats besides its native one. The search functionality will be based on <a href=\"/Chess_Query_Language\" title=\"Chess Query Language\">CQL</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#File_Formats\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">File Formats</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2013_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2013 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"File_Formats\">File Formats</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scidb&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: File Formats\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> Scidb .sci, .scv</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/SCID\" title=\"SCID\">Scid</a> .si3, .si4</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/ChessBase_(Database)\" title=\"ChessBase (Database)\">ChessBase</a> .cbh, .cbf (read-only)</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Portable_Game_Notation\" title=\"Portable Game Notation\">PGN</a> .pgn, .pgn.gz, .zip</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scidb&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/ChessX\" title=\"ChessX\">ChessX</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jose&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jose (page does not exist)\">jose</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/SCID\" title=\"SCID\">SCID</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Scid_vs._PC\" title=\"Scid vs. PC\">Scid vs. PC</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scidb&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2013_...\">2013 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scidb&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2013 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48270\">Help installing scidb</a> by Aloisio Ponti, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 14, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49492\">Scidb - porting to Mac OS X</a> by <a href=\"/Norbert_Raimund_Leisner\" title=\"Norbert Raimund Leisner\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 28, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.mail-archive.com/scid-users@lists.sourceforge.net/msg06639.html\">Scid.eco</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Gregor_Cramer&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Gregor Cramer (page does not exist)\">Gregor Cramer</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.mail-archive.com/scid-users@lists.sourceforge.net/\">scid-users</a>, April 19, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/ECO\" title=\"ECO\">ECO</a>, <a href=\"/SCID\" title=\"SCID\">SCID</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scidb&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58820\">Scidb binary file format</a> by <a href=\"/Dominik_Klein\" title=\"Dominik Klein\">Dominik Klein</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 05, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=60288\">Scidb on linux mint</a> by <a href=\"/Ferdinand_Mosca\" title=\"Ferdinand Mosca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 27, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61165\">Scid / Scid vs. PC - ChessBase (.ctg) and Arena (.abk)</a> by <a href=\"/Norbert_Raimund_Leisner\" title=\"Norbert Raimund Leisner\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/CTG\" title=\"CTG\">CTG</a>, <a href=\"/ABK\" title=\"ABK\">ABK</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=64938\">Scidb release 1431</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Gregor_Cramer&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Gregor Cramer (page does not exist)\">Gregor Cramer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 20, 2017</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scidb&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://scidb.sourceforge.net/index.html\">Welcome to Scidb</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://sourceforge.net/projects/scidb/\">Scidb | Free Games software downloads at SourceForge.net</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://sourceforge.net/p/scidb/mailman/scidb-users/\">Scidb / Mailing Lists</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scidb&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://scidb.sourceforge.net/screenshots.html\">Scidb - Screenshots</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.mail-archive.com/scid-users@lists.sourceforge.net/msg06020.html\">Re: Testing</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Gregor_Cramer&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Gregor Cramer (page does not exist)\">Gregor Cramer</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.mail-archive.com/scid-users@lists.sourceforge.net/\">scid-users</a>, January 04, 2013</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://scidb.sourceforge.net/index.html\">Welcome to Scidb</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Databases\" title=\"Databases\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!